                             'SoliTri' 1.21

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'SoliTri' is a solitaire type of @{" game " link play}, it is based on
'Tri-Peaks' where the game board consists of 28 cards that are
placed in 3 overlapping pyramids. A card (the 'next' card), facing
up is shown at the bottom under the game board. At the left of that
card is a pack of the remaining cards and that pack is face down.
A number indicates how many cards are remaining in that pack.

  The goal of the game is to empty all the pyramids by clicking on
cards that are higher or lower by one unit than the next card at
the bottom of the window. For example, if the card is a 7 of Heart,
the choosen card should be a 6 or 8, the colour or type of figure
has no importance.

  Have fun!

